From 7845d7cc1c3915f70545cd183d33a1978c049c8a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 15:31:56 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 42/84] Trace PDF wrapper parsing

The wrapper knocked in HTML shoes,
But parser crumbs gave scanty clues.
Now logs mark each quiet door,
Till shadow roots can hide no more.
---
 .../blink/renderer/core/dom/document_init.cc  |  62 ++++-
 .../core/html/html_frame_owner_element.cc     | 152 +++++++++---
 .../html/parser/html_construction_site.cc     | 100 +++++---
 .../renderer/core/loader/document_loader.cc   | 216 +++++++++++++-----
 4 files changed, 393 insertions(+), 137 deletions(-)

